---
title: Cashflow — Isolamento Ledger × Consolidation (NFR-A-01)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Op as Operador (make chaos-validate)
    actor Merchant as Merchant (100 POSTs)
    participant API as Ledger.Api
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Outbox)
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant WRK as Consolidation.Worker
    participant MGO as MongoDB

    note over Op: Fase 1 — derruba Consolidation
    Op->>WRK: docker compose stop consolidation-worker
    Op->>MGO: docker compose stop mongo
    Op->>API: (consolidation-api também parado)

    note over Op,Merchant: Fase 2 — 100 POSTs em Ledger (alvo: 100/100 = 201)
    loop 100 vezes
        Merchant->>+API: POST /api/v1/entries<br/>JWT + Idempotency-Key
        API->>+DB: BEGIN<br/>INSERT entry + idempotency_key + OutboxMessage<br/>COMMIT
        DB-->>-API: OK
        API-->>-Merchant: 201 Created
    end
    note over API,DB: Outbox cresce ~100 msgs pending<br/>(broker disponível mas worker offline →<br/>publish OK, consume parado)

    note over MQ: Mensagens enfileiradas no RabbitMQ<br/>(durable queue, persistent delivery)

    note over Op: Fase 3 — restaura Consolidation
    Op->>MGO: docker compose start mongo
    Op->>WRK: docker compose start consolidation-worker
    Op->>API: (consolidation-api também restart)

    rect rgb(245, 250, 245)
    note over WRK,MGO: Worker drena backlog idempotente
        loop até processed_events alcançar 100
            WRK->>+MQ: Consume EntryRegisteredV1
            MQ-->>-WRK: message
            WRK->>+MGO: FindOneAndUpdate atomic<br/>filter $ne LastEventId<br/>$inc totals + $set lastEventId
            MGO-->>-WRK: upsert / no-op (replay safe)
        end
    end

    note over Op: Fase 4 — verifica catch-up
    Op->>+API: GET /balances/{merchantId}/daily?date=2026-05-13
    API->>MGO: findOne daily_balance
    MGO-->>API: doc com entriesCount = 100
    API-->>-Op: 200 OK

    Note over Op,MGO: Saída real 100/100 201. Catch-up em ~22s (timeout 90s). NFR-A-01 OK. Ledger continuou aceitando entries com Consolidation completamente offline.
